import React, { useState } from 'react'
import AutocompletCorrespondant from './Autocomplet'
import { Form } from 'semantic-ui-react'



export default function presentation() {
    const [informations, setInformations] = useState({
        name: "",
        surname: "",
        homme: "",
        femme: "",
        doctegestio: "",
        doctocare: "",
        amapa: "",
        poppins: "",

    })

    const handleChange = (e, { value }) => setInformations({ ...informations, [e.target.name]: value })

    return (
        <Form>
            <Form.Group inline>
                <Form.Input fluid label='Prenom' placeholder='Prenom' />
                <Form.Input fluid label='Nom' placeholder='Nom' />
                <Form.Radio
                    name="homme"
                    label='Homme'
                    value='homme'
                    checked={value === 'homme'}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                />
                <Form.Radio
                    name="femme"
                    label='Femme'
                    value='femme'
                    checked={value === 'femme'}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                />
            </Form.Group>
            <Form.Group inline>
                <label>Op√©rateurs ?</label>
                <Checkbox label='doctegestio' />
                {/* <Form.Radio
                    name="doctegestio"
                    label='Doctegestio'
                    value='doctegestio'
                    checked={value === 'doctegestio'}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                />
                <Form.Radio
                    name="doctocare"
                    label='Doctocare'
                    value='doctocare'
                    checked={value === 'doctocare'}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                />
                <Form.Radio
                    name="amapa"
                    label='Amapa'
                    value='amapa'
                    checked={value === 'amapa'}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                />
                <Form.Radio
                    name="poppins"
                    label='Poppins'
                    value='poppins'
                    checked={value === 'poppins'}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                /> */}
                <AutocompletCorrespondant />
            </Form.Group>
        </Form>
    )
}
